title: Cafe Oasis
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Chinese, Juice bar, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Little restaurant next to the Asian Market, it is on the second floor. Has a very modern vibe. The menu features a vegetarian section with tofu dishes and vegetable stir-fried dishes. There are also vegetarian appetizers and soups. Bubble teas. 10% off with a student ID. Has Wi-Fi.
